      "updated": 1784703706
    },
    {
      "id": "6a606ada0000000000294bb6",
      "text": "from [2025/07/16]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1784703706,
      "updated": 1784703706
    },
    {
      "id": "6a606ada0000000000294bb8",
      "text": "勝手宮崎駿…[terang.icon]",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1784703706,
      "updated": 1784703709
    },
    {
      "id": "6a606ada0000000000294bb9",
      "text": "\t>おい！やめろ！やめろ！",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1784703706,
      "updated": 1784703708
    },
    {
      "id": "6a606ada0000000000294bba",
      "text": " >謎の中国メーカーが1/12スケールアクションフィギュアで[宮崎駿]を勝手に出すな！",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1784703706,
      "updated": 1784703708
    },
    {
      "id": "6a606ada0000000000294bbb",
      "text": " >無駄に面白いのを止めろ！",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1784703706,
      "updated": 1784703708
    },
    {
      "id": "6a606ada0000000000294bbc",
      "text": " >何がグランドマスターだ！駿じゃねえか！",
      "userId": "5d69dde930e3c500170f1ffd",
      "created": 1784703706,
      "updated": 1784703708
    },
    {
      "id": "6a606ada0000000000294bbd",
